{
  "stem": "8916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good afternoon, Stella.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Labol ?] Leyson.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Labol.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My Hebrew was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Arya. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in 1929.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 15.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 66.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in a small town in eastern Poland called Narewka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Moshe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother's name was Anna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a machinist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was tool and dye maker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He started in Narewka, and then he eventually transferred with a company to a place called Krakow, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, from Narewka, Krakow was approximately 350 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he actually as a young man left Narewka to seek his fortune in Krakow, because in a small town like Narewka, there was not too many opportunities for a young man at his age.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in his 30s, and so when the company moved, he was asked to relocate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he left Narewka and his family and went to establish himself in the big city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- would have been very difficult to-- for a young man in his 30s just getting started to take his family to a big city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- besides, in those days, people didn't move very much, and my mother thought that it would be easier for her with five children to stay in Narewka, where she had her-- her parents, my grandparents, and my father's parents.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we children were looked after by both grandparents, and so it was much easier that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was thought that it was-- wasn't going to be very long before he could bring his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was a-- an easygoing kind of father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he encouraged us, but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was not of an aggressive kind of person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Patient.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
